---
import MainHead from '../components/MainHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer/index.jsx';
import Nav from '../components/Nav/index.jsx';
---

<html lang="en">

<head>
	<MainHead title="About" description="About me" />
	<style lang="scss">
		.heroImg {
			height: 30rem;
			width: auto;
			background-repeat: no-repeat;
			background-size: contain;
			background-position: center;
			overflow: hidden;
			background-image: url("../../public/assets/profile.jpg");
		}

		.bio {
			font-size: var(--f-u1);
			line-height: 2;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<Nav />
	<div class="wrapper">
		<h1>About me</h1>
		<div class="heroImg">
		</div>
		<div class="bio wrapper wrapper__readable mt8">
			<p>
				Hi!
			</p>
			<p>Thanks for checking out my website. My name is Dennis and i am from a small island named Zakynthos i Greece.
			</p>
			<p>
				Being a massive technology nerd, i was into computers from a very young age.
				When we started doing programming in school, it was easily my favourite subject.
				I really love problem solving, what can i sayüòÅ
			</p>
			<p>
				So i decided to studie Computer Science at Ionian University in Corfu. Where i learned a lot of different programming languages, programming theories, technologies and much more.
			</p>
			<p>
				After doing my internship at a company for web development, i started aiming to become a web developer myself.
			</p>
			<p>
				So here I am, finally feeling confident enough in my skills to look for a job. Wish me luck! üòä
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<Footer />
</body>

</html>
